{"tid":386602,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"港姐冠軍雷莊𠒇開估： 攞身份證寫錯咗 兒做𠒇，到參選先發覺 遲D會去改番","createTime":"2017-09-04T04:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T12:18:58.000Z","uid":22349,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7c76aa5693514d791798fa734144a99818c722bc","tid":386602,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:08:08.000Z","msg":"雷莊𠒇說：「其實我當年攞身份證嗰陣一直冇發覺，原來喺嗰刻已經寫錯咗，到我參選，我仲問大會做乜寫錯我名，佢哋話係跟住我身份證咁寫，我先發覺寫錯咗，我遲啲會去改番！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mybb.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/bkn-20170903232158463-0903_00862_001_06b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mybb.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2Fbkn-20170903232158463-0903_00862_001_06b.jpg&h=86a891a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb7437887db366bc881856b3e316d2e377cb995d","tid":386602,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:09:08.000Z","msg":"香港小姐2017終於塵埃落定，冠軍由23歲來自多倫多的雷莊𠒇，原來老豆雷葆文係香港的十大傑出設計師， 人稱「設計多面手」，而且身家十分富有，香港及海外都擁有物業，傳聞係億億聲，在商界有頭有面。雷莊𠒇曾表示父親十分支持她參選，當然佢自己都十分有料到，作為唯一嘅海外突入佳麗，身高成5呎7寸，身材更加是十分惹火，因為佢係模特兒出身㗎！"},{"pid":"cfc29a1dbec437a36ce15d522d5dc058397d5799","tid":386602,"uid":934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:16:01.000Z","msg":"個兜字點打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e7ee3c9f1b50cdc69eda273c204d9c5506801c","tid":386602,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T05:35:17.000Z","msg":"負責將𠒇輸入電腦果條友都幾勁wo<br />\n咁生僻嘅字都識"},{"pid":"bd5a6578b0ea32833ae56c929b49a40c5fc0a06e","tid":386602,"uid":22566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T05:38:31.000Z","msg":"其實係咩字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e3e28663e5a0b7b270587b334b777a2cc104a5","tid":386602,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T05:42:15.000Z",